title: US airman who thwarted French train attack stabbed
text:
> Top News US airman who thwarted French train attack stabbed This frame from video provided by A&P Liquors, shows a group of people, including U.S. airman Spencer Stone, fighting outside a bar in Sacramento, Calif., in the early hours of Thursday, Oct. 8, 2015. Stone, who helped stop a terror attack on a French train in August, was stabbed and wounded, but is expected to survive. (A&P Liquors via AP) iWitness7 is your chance to join the News Center 7 team!
